    Association between Visceral Fat Area and Cancer Prognosis: A Population-Based Multicenter Prospective Study.
 VFA is an independent prognostic indicator of muscle mass in patients with diverse types of cancer, particularly gastric, colorectal, and non-small cell lung cancers.
